'''砂拉越日''' ({{lang-ms|Hari Sarawak}}; {{lang-en|Sarawak Day}}) 定于每年的7月22日，受到[[砂拉越|砂拉越]]政府及砂拉越人民的广泛重视。<ref name="ND">{{Cite book|url=http://discovery.nationalarchives.gov.uk/details/r/C10991834|title=砂拉越，沙巴和新加坡宣布独立|archivedate=2021-04-13|publisher=The National Archives|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413063451/https://discovery.nationalarchives.gov.uk/details/r/C10991834|access-date=2021-01-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="discovery.nationalarchives.gov.uk">{{cite web|url=http://discovery.nationalarchives.gov.uk/details/r/C760803|title=The National Archives DO 169/254 (Constitutional issues in respect of North Borneo and Sarawak on joining the federation)|publisher=[[英国国家档案馆|英国国家档案馆]]|date=1961–1963|accessdate=23 April 2015|archive-date=2019-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527103336/https://discovery.nationalarchives.gov.uk/details/r/C760803|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Vernon L. Porritt|title=British Colonial Rule in Sarawak, 1946-1963|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=4pBwAAAAMAAJ|year=1997|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-983-56-0009-8|access-date=2015-07-25|archive-date=2016-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617152249/https://books.google.com/books?id=4pBwAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Philip Mathews|title=Chronicle of Malaysia: Fifty Years of Headline News, 1963-2013|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=md9UAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA15|date=28 February 2014|publisher=Editions Didier Millet|isbn=978-967-10617-4-9|pages=15–|access-date=2015-07-25|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512125941/https://books.google.com/books?id=md9UAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://asiapacific.anu.edu.au/newmandala/2013/07/27/sarawaks-independence-day/|title=Sarawak’s "Independence Day"|publisher=[[Australian_National_University|Australian National University]]|work=New Mandala|date=27 July 2013|accessdate=30 May 2014|author=Murray Hunter|archive-date=2015-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725120609/http://asiapacific.anu.edu.au/newmandala/2013/07/27/sarawaks-independence-day/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mysinchew.com/node/76245|title=Tanah airku - My homeland - 美丽的国家|publisher=[[星洲日报|星洲日报]]|date=6 August 2012|accessdate=31 May 2014|author=Bob Teoh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140530161825/http://www.mysinchew.com/node/76245|archivedate=2014年5月30日|deadurl=no}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
1841年，文莱帝国授予[[砂拉越王国|砂拉越王国]]独立的地位，自1888年，其被英国保护。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.ijern.com/journal/January-2014/46.pdf|title=Borneo Art Education - BAE|author=Aloysius Yapp|journal=International Journal of Education and Research|date=January 2014|volume=II|issue=1|pages=2|ISSN=2201-6333|format=[[PDF|PDF]]|access-date=2015-07-25|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924033444/http://www.ijern.com/journal/January-2014/46.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而，在那个时候，砂拉越并未获得“完全独立”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/opinion/khairie-hisyam-aliman/article/no-sarawak-did-not-gain-independence-in-1841|title=No, Sarawak did not gain independence in 1841|author=Khairie Hisyam Aliman|publisher=The Malay Mail|date=13 September 2014|accessdate=15 September 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915014609/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/opinion/khairie-hisyam-aliman/article/no-sarawak-did-not-gain-independence-in-1841|archivedate=2014年9月15日|deadurl=no}}</ref> [[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]结束后，其领土被英国军事管制区接管，且在1946年成为了英殖民地。<ref>{{cite book|author1=Patricia Pui Huen Lim|author2=Diana Wong|title=War and Memory in Malaysia and Singapore|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ADkiembZcLYC&pg=PA124|year=2000|publisher=Institute of Southeast Asian Studies|isbn=978-981-230-037-9|pages=124–}}</ref> 领土转移给殖民政府引起了砂拉越人民的不满，人民期望能够获得独立，开展了反割让运动（Anti-cession movement of Sarawak）1949年，英国第二任驻砂总督被马来年轻老师罗斯利多比（Rosli Dhobi）暗杀<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-17299633|title=The stabbed governor of Sarawak|author=Mike Thompson|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=12 March 2012|accessdate=30 May 2014|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924123649/http://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-17299633|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theborneopost.com/2013/09/22/farewell-to-the-crown-prince/|title=Farewell to the Crown Prince|author=Antonia Chiam|publisher=The Borneo Post|date=22 September 2013|accessdate=30 May 2014|archive-date=2018-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925164710/http://www.theborneopost.com/2013/09/22/farewell-to-the-crown-prince/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。总督继任者为安东尼安东尼·阿贝尔（Anthony Abell），是科博德委员会（Cobbold Commission）的成员之一。

砂拉越是于1963年7月22日获得“自治权”的<ref name="discovery.nationalarchives.gov.uk"/>，且以砂拉越将会在同年9月16日共组马来西亚为前提<ref>{{cite book|author=Frans Welman|title=Borneo Trilogy Sarawak: Volume 2|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=A-H-O8pxUnMC&pg=PA134|publisher=Booksmango|isbn=978-616-245-089-1|pages=134–|access-date=2015-07-25|archive-date=2015-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322134650/http://books.google.com/books?id=A-H-O8pxUnMC&pg=PA134|dead-url=no}}</ref> 砂拉越自治前的最后一名英籍总督是Alexander Waddell，<ref>'Sarawakiana' 26 August 2008 "The last British governor of Sarawak'</ref> ，而首名砂拉越人[[首席部长|首席部长]]由英殖民政府任命，为Stephen Kalong Ningkan<ref>{{cite book|title=Asia Yearbook|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=IdZHAAAAYAAJ|year=1964|publisher=Far Eastern economic review|access-date=2015-07-25|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519080457/https://books.google.com/books?id=IdZHAAAAYAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

